metadata.title: Customized Solutions Please Keep Gate Closed - Dogs in Yard - 8" X 12" Aluminum - UV Resistant Coating
features: High gloss aluminum with UV protective coating.
8" x 12" with two pre drilled holes on each side for mounting.
Rounded corners for safety and professional appearance.
High quality detailed sublimated printing that becomes part of the aluminum. This is NOT vinyl lettering.
description: Let visitors know to keep the gate closed because a dog is on your premises. Sign is made of aluminum and is suitable for indoor or outdoor use. Will not rust.
